snippet.title: Aaero - Revenge (4K | Xbox One X)
snippet.description:
So turns out that the first patch didn't give us full 4K but it's here now! and IT. LOOKS. STUNNING!

I'll never delete this game XD

Game: Aaero
Music: Revenge by Habstrakt & Megalodon

Review: http://thisgengaming.com/2017/07/28/aaero-review/

Buy it now!
Steam: https://www.humblebundle.com/store/aaero?partner=bloodyspasm
Xbox One: https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/store/p/aaero/bzr51xd70nkd 
PS4: https://www.playstation.com/en-us/games/aaero-ps4/
